4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals seeking to enter the field without prior knowledge. Over 16 weeks, participants engage in three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 attendees per class. The curriculum covers essential topics like Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. Students will learn to manage risks and navigate compliance with international standards. An official completion certificate is awarded. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop